---
title: Smart Double Chicken Crunch Salad with Peanuts and Edamame
description: Wholesome coleslaw mix and crisp sweet bell peppers add fun to every bite of this salad. Soy and mirin combine in a sweet, sticky glaze that dresses lean ground chicken and protein-rich edamame.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-croquante-au-poulet-double-652c12e0.jpg
